name: Mirtazapine - 03 Special Edition (Ghost series collection)
description:
Mirtazapine - 01 (Ghost series collection)
Special colorised (Red & Blue) version of Mirtazapine ghost series. Grungy black&white noise and feedback . Created with self-built, modular generative video performance tool (built in Quartz Composer) . Ghost series collection, circa 2011 .
